    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"rest\" feels so impossible when the world keeps moving. i look at the people around me—my advisors, my peers—and they all have these clear paths. i just feel like a burden, like a mistake in the system. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be if the noise just stopped... if i didn't have to carry this Version of myself anymore. does it ever just... go away? the weight of it all?",
